{{Infobox journal | title = Gesta | cover = Gesta cover.png | image_size = 200px | editor = Linda Safran, Adam S. Cohen | discipline = [[Art history]] | abbreviation = Gesta | publisher = [[University of Chicago Press]] | country = | history = 1963-present | frequency = Biannual | website = http://www.journals.uchicago.edu/ges | link1 = | link1-name = | ISSN = 0016-920X | eISSN = 2169-3099 | JSTOR = 0016920X | LCCN = 65005114 | OCLC = 1606201 }} '''''Gesta''''' is a [[peer-review]]ed [[academic journal]] in the area of [[medieval art]]. It was established in 1963 and is published by the [[University of Chicago Press]]. The [[editors-in-chief]] are Linda Safran ([[Pontifical Institute of Mediaeval Studies]]) and Adam S. Cohen ([[University of Toronto]]).
